status: MARC21-008: Original alphabet or script of title of continuing resource
the original alphabet or script of the language of the title on the source item upon which the key title is based.

preferred label (en): no alphabet or script given/no key title

definition (en): Original alphabet or script of title other than basic Roman, extended Roman, cyrillic, Japanese, Chinese, Arabic, Greek, Hebrew, Thai, Devanagari,Korean, Tamil.
